            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Imperator Caesar Flavius Valentinianus Pius Felix victor <lb n="2"/>ac triumfator semper Augustus et Flavius Valens Pius Felix <lb n="3"/>victor ac triumfator semper Augustus et Flavius Gratianus <lb n="4"/>Pius Felix victor ac triumfator semper Augustus Reginis suis <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>hermas vetustate et terrae motu conlabsas <note>sic</note> in meliorem <lb n="6"/>cultum formamque auspiciis felicioribus reddiderunt <lb n="7"/>reddita basilica marmorum quae <supplied reason="lost">n</supplied>umquam habuerat <lb n="8"/>pulc<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ritudine</abbr></expan> decorata nova etiam porticu adiecta curante <lb n="9"/>Pontio Attico <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> correctore Lucaniae et Brittiorum <note>sic</note> dedecatas <note>sic</note> <lb n="10"/>quartum Kalendarum Iuliarum die domino nostro Gratiano <lb n="11"/>Augusto tertio et Flavio Equitio <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> consulibus
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p/>
            </div>
